Source: scratchbox2
Maintainer: Riku Voipio <riku.voipio@iki.fi>
Section: utils
Priority: extra
Standards-Version: 3.7.2
Build-Depends: debhelper (>=5), automake1.9, autoconf

Package: scratchbox2
Architecture: i386 amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Recommends: qemu
Suggests: sbrsh
Description: Transparent crosscompiling enviroinment
 Scratchbox2 uses LD_PRELOAD library to create a transparent crosscompiling
 enviroinment. Scratchbox2 automatically maps filesystem access to 
 crosscompiler, target libraries and headers using a flexible lua path mapping 
 engine. Together with cpu transparency, it enables fast crosscompiling
 without modifying build scripts.
